data.description: Attention Investors! With some work, this could make a great short-term rental. Or someone could make this their hunting cabin. Close to the river but without the high price of waterfront. Only about 30 minutes to both Madison and the Dells. Two 19'x19' areas at the end of the house that can be workshops or potentially a small garage. Wall furnaces run on LP or use the wood-burner for heat instead. Will not likely qualify for most loan programs.
